{
  "version": "0.4",
  "title": "XCP Service: Documentary Business Storytelling — Sub-page",
  "type": "page",
  "content": [
    {
      "id": "doc_hero",
      "elType": "section",
      "settings": {
        "_title": "Documentary Hero",
        "layout": "full_width",
        "background_image": {
          "url": "[uc_local]assets/images/documentary-hero.jpg"
        },
        "content_position": "middle"
      },
      "elements": [
        {
          "id": "doc_hero_col",
          "elType": "column",
          "settings": {
            "_column_size": 100
          },
          "elements": [
            {
              "id": "doc_eyebrow",
              "elType": "widget",
              "widgetType": "text-editor",
              "settings": {
                "editor": "<p>Documentary Business Storytelling</p>"
              }
            },
            {
              "id": "doc_title",
              "elType": "widget",
              "widgetType": "heading",
              "settings": {
                "title": "Your Business, Captured as It Really Is",
                "header_size": "h1",
                "align": "center"
              }
            },
            {
              "id": "doc_subtitle",
              "elType": "widget",
              "widgetType": "text-editor",
              "settings": {
                "editor": "<p>Documentary business photography is unposed, candid, and honest. It captures your team at work, your process in motion, and the authentic culture that makes your business worth choosing.</p>"
              }
            },
            {
              "id": "doc_cta_button",
              "elType": "widget",
              "widgetType": "button",
              "settings": {
                "text": "Enquire About Documentary Coverage",
                "link": {
                  "url": "/contact",
                  "is_external": false,
                  "nofollow": false
                },
                "align": "center"
              }
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "doc_overview",
      "elType": "section",
      "settings": {
        "_title": "Documentary Overview",
        "layout": "boxed",
        "structure": "20"
      },
      "elements": [
        {
          "id": "doc_overview_image_col",
          "elType": "column",
          "settings": {
            "_column_size": 40,
            "_column_size_tablet": 100,
            "_column_size_mobile": 100
          },
          "elements": [
            {
              "id": "doc_overview_image",
              "elType": "widget",
              "widgetType": "image",
              "settings": {
                "image": {
                  "url": "[uc_local]assets/images/documentary-overview.jpg"
                },
                "image_size": "large"
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "doc_overview_text_col",
          "elType": "column",
          "settings": {
            "_column_size": 60,
            "_column_size_tablet": 100,
            "_column_size_mobile": 100
          },
          "elements": [
            {
              "id": "doc_overview_heading",
              "elType": "widget",
              "widgetType": "heading",
              "settings": {
                "title": "What Documentary Business Photography Looks Like",
                "header_size": "h2"
              }
            },
            {
              "id": "doc_overview_text",
              "elType": "widget",
              "widgetType": "text-editor",
              "settings": {
                "editor": "<p>Where brand photography is curated and art-directed, documentary photography follows the reality of your working day. It captures the energy, the detail, the moments of concentration and connection that tell your real story.</p><p>This is particularly powerful for businesses that want to demonstrate authenticity — creative agencies, studios, hospitality businesses, makers, performers, and organisations with a strong culture and community.</p><ul><li>Unposed, candid coverage of your working environment</li><li>Team portraits in context (not forced against a plain background)</li><li>Process and craft documentation</li><li>Events, launches, and behind-the-scenes coverage</li><li>Multi-day projects available for deeper storytelling</li><li>Delivered as a curated library of 60–120 images</li><li>Full commercial licence included</li></ul>"
              }
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "doc_closing_cta",
      "elType": "section",
      "settings": {
        "_title": "Documentary Closing CTA",
        "layout": "boxed"
      },
      "elements": [
        {
          "id": "doc_closing_col",
          "elType": "column",
          "settings": {
            "_column_size": 100,
            "text_align": "center"
          },
          "elements": [
            {
              "id": "doc_closing_heading",
              "elType": "widget",
              "widgetType": "heading",
              "settings": {
                "title": "Ready to Document Your Story?",
                "header_size": "h2",
                "align": "center"
              }
            },
            {
              "id": "doc_closing_text",
              "elType": "widget",
              "widgetType": "text-editor",
              "settings": {
                "editor": "<p>Documentary projects are scoped individually. Tell me about your business and what you want to capture, and I will propose an approach that fits your team, your environment, and your budget.</p>"
              }
            },
            {
              "id": "doc_closing_button",
              "elType": "widget",
              "widgetType": "button",
              "settings": {
                "text": "Start the Conversation",
                "link": {
                  "url": "/contact",
                  "is_external": false,
                  "nofollow": false
                },
                "align": "center"
              }
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
